{"id": "anc_modal_open", "modality": "animations", "name": "Modal Open", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a modal dialog. Over ~2.5s a dim backdrop fades in over a content page, then a centered modal card scales-and-fades up from 90% to 100%, containing a title, two lines of body text, and a right-aligned row of two buttons (Cancel, Confirm). The modal stays centered and fully on screen.", "requirements": ["The modal card is horizontally and vertically centered and fully within the viewport once shown", "The modal grows in over time (scale increases across early frames) then settles", "The modal content (title, body, buttons) stays inside the modal card (no overflow)", "The two buttons are right-aligned in one row inside the modal and do not overlap", "A dim backdrop covers the page behind the modal in the settled frames", "No scrollbar appears at any frame"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 14, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2665, "rv_n_defects": 16, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 13359}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 9, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2554, "rv_n_defects": 8, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 13026}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 8, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2593, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 11304}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_modal_open_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_modal_open_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Modal Dialog Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Background content page */\n        .content-page {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            padding: 80px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .page-header {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .page-title {\n            font-size: 72px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            letter-spacing: -2px;\n        }\n\n        .page-subtitle {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            font-weight: 300;\n        }\n\n        .content-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n            gap: 40px;\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .content-card {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .card-text {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        /* Modal backdrop */\n        .modal-backdrop {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: backdropFadeIn 1.2s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        /* Modal container */\n        .modal-container {\n            transform: scale(0.9);\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: modalScaleIn 1.3s ease-out 1.2s forwards;\n        }\n\n        /* Modal card */\n        .modal-card {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            width: 560px;\n            padding: 48px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .modal-title {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            letter-spacing: -1px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-body {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-text {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: #4a4a4a;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-text:last-child {\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n\n        .modal-buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: flex-end;\n            gap: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-button {\n            padding: 14px 32px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.2s ease;\n            min-width: 120px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-button.cancel {\n            background: #f5f5f5;\n            color: #666;\n            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        .modal-button.cancel:hover {\n            background: #ebebeb;\n            border-color: #d0d0d0;\n        }\n\n        .modal-button.confirm {\n            background: #667eea;\n            color: white;\n            border: 2px solid #667eea;\n        }\n\n        .modal-button.confirm:hover {\n            background: #5a6fd8;\n            border-color: #5a6fd8;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes backdropFadeIn {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes modalScaleIn {\n            from {\n                transform: scale(0.9);\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            to {\n                transform: scale(1);\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- Background content page -->\n    <div class=\"content-page\">\n        <div class=\"page-header\">\n            <h1 class=\"page-title\">Dashboard</h1>\n            <p class=\"page-subtitle\">Manage your projects and settings</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-grid\">\n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Projects</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">View and manage all your active projects. Track progress, assign tasks, and collaborate with your team members.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Analytics</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Get insights into your performance metrics. Monitor key indicators and make data-driven decisions for your business.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Settings</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Customize your workspace preferences. Configure notifications, security settings, and integration options.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Team</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Manage team members and permissions. Invite new collaborators and organize your workspace structure.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Reports</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Generate comprehensive reports on your activities. Export data and share insights with stakeholders.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Support</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Access help resources and contact our support team. Find documentation, tutorials, and troubleshooting guides.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Modal backdrop and dialog -->\n    <div class=\"modal-backdrop\">\n        <div class=\"modal-container\">\n            <div class=\"modal-card\">\n                <h2 class=\"modal-title\">Confirm Action</h2>\n                <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                    <p class=\"modal-text\">Are you sure you want to delete this project? This action cannot be undone and will permanently remove all associated data.</p>\n                    <p class=\"modal-text\">All team members will lose access to this project and its resources immediately.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"modal-buttons\">\n                    <button class=\"modal-button cancel\">Cancel</button>\n                    <button class=\"modal-button confirm\">Confirm</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Modal Dialog Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        /* Background content page */\n        .content-page {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            padding: 80px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .page-header {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .page-title {\n            font-size: 72px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            letter-spacing: -2px;\n        }\n\n        .page-subtitle {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            font-weight: 300;\n        }\n\n        .content-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n            gap: 40px;\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .content-card {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .card-text {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        /* Modal backdrop */\n        .modal-backdrop {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: fadeInBackdrop 1.2s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        /* Modal container */\n        .modal {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            width: 600px;\n            max-width: 90vw;\n            padding: 48px;\n            transform: scale(0.9);\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: scaleInModal 1.3s ease-out 1.2s forwards;\n        }\n\n        .modal-title {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2d3748;\n            margin-bottom: 32px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .modal-body {\n            margin-bottom: 48px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-text {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: #4a5568;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .modal-text:last-child {\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n\n        .modal-actions {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: flex-end;\n            gap: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            padding: 16px 32px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.2s ease;\n            min-width: 120px;\n        }\n\n        .btn-cancel {\n            background: #e2e8f0;\n            color: #4a5568;\n        }\n\n        .btn-cancel:hover {\n            background: #cbd5e0;\n        }\n\n        .btn-confirm {\n            background: #667eea;\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .btn-confirm:hover {\n            background: #5a67d8;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes fadeInBackdrop {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scaleInModal {\n            from {\n                transform: scale(0.9);\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            to {\n                transform: scale(1);\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- Background content page -->\n    <div class=\"content-page\">\n        <div class=\"page-header\">\n            <h1 class=\"page-title\">Dashboard</h1>\n            <p class=\"page-subtitle\">Welcome to your workspace</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-grid\">\n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Analytics</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">View detailed insights and performance metrics for your projects and campaigns.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Projects</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Manage your active projects, collaborate with team members, and track progress.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Settings</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Configure your account preferences, notifications, and security settings.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Reports</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Generate comprehensive reports and export data for further analysis.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Team</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Invite team members, assign roles, and manage workspace permissions.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content-card\">\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Support</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">Access help documentation, contact support, and view system status updates.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Modal backdrop and dialog -->\n    <div class=\"modal-backdrop\">\n        <div class=\"modal\">\n            <h2 class=\"modal-title\">Confirm Action</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                <p class=\"modal-text\">Are you sure you want to proceed with this action? This operation cannot be undone and will affect your current workspace settings.</p>\n                <p class=\"modal-text\">Please review your selection carefully before confirming to avoid any unintended changes to your data.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"modal-actions\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-cancel\">Cancel</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-confirm\">Confirm</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}